<lb n="0422b07"/><head type="no">No. 1304</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0422b08"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0422004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】享保年間刊長谷寺藏本，【甲】康元二年寫東寺三密藏本</note>宿曜<note n="0422005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">儀軌＝軌儀【甲】</note><app n="0422005"><lem>儀軌</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">軌儀</rdg></app>一卷</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0422b09"/>
<lb n="0422b10"/><byline type="Author">一行撰</byline>
<lb n="0422b11"/><p>虛空藏印　合掌縛水指。風指如寶形。真言
<lb n="0422b12"/>曰</p>
<lb n="0422b13"/><p type="dharani">唵阿伽沙<note place="inline">一</note>迦羅波伊野<note place="inline">二</note>唵麼哩<note place="inline">三</note>伽摩哩<note place="inline">四</note>
<lb n="0422b14"/>母梨<note place="inline">五</note>娑<note n="0422006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00085;＝婆【甲】</note><app n="0422006"><lem>&CB00085;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">婆</rdg></app>賀</p>
<lb n="0422b15"/><p>若人欲求福智。當歸依此菩薩。日月<note n="0422007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">星＋（宿）【甲】</note><app n="0422007"><lem>星</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">星宿</rdg></app>。皆
<lb n="0422b16"/>虛空藏所變也</p>
<lb n="0422b17"/><p>文殊印　虛<note n="0422008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">空＝心【甲】</note><app n="0422008"><lem>空</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">心</rdg></app>合掌。以<note n="0422009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">大＝二火【甲】</note><app n="0422009"><lem>大</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">二火</rdg></app>指各押二水甲。
<lb n="0422b18"/>二風屈捻空端。真言曰</p>
<lb n="0422b19"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">引</note>阿<note place="inline">引入惡聲</note>味<note place="inline">引</note><note n="0422010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">羅＝囉【甲】＊</note><app n="0422010"><lem>羅</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">囉</rdg></app>吽佉左<note n="0422011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">洛＝&CB00080;【甲】</note><app n="0422011"><lem>洛</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB00080;</rdg></app>　若求息<note n="0422012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">災字甲本作本文</note><note n="0422012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（災）夾註＝（災）本文【甲】</note><app n="0422012"><lem><note place="inline">災</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">災</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0422b20"/><p>當欲<note n="0422013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">殄＝珍【甲】</note><app n="0422013"><lem>殄</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">珍</rdg></app>滅七種災難。所謂日月薄<note n="0422014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00068;＝&CB14291;【甲】</note><app n="0422014"><lem>&CB00068;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB14291;</rdg></app>五星。
<lb n="0422b21"/>違失常度兵賊競起。水旱不時風雨失度。惡
<lb n="0422b22"/>臣背逆損害國民。<note n="0422015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">武＝虎&M062403;【原】，〔武〕－【甲】</note><app n="0422015"><lem>武</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">虎</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>狼惡獸食噉眾生。五穀
<lb n="0422b23"/>不登。如是災禍急厄官府王難死厄<note n="0422016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（怕）＋怖【甲】</note><app n="0422016"><lem>怖</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">怕怖</rdg></app>等。皆
<lb n="0422b24"/>當消散</p>
<lb n="0422b25"/><p>普賢印　虛心合掌真言曰</p>
<lb n="0422b26"/><p type="dharani">支波啄<note place="inline">一決定</note>毘尼波啄<note place="inline">二斷結</note>鳥蘇波啄<note place="inline">三盡生死</note></p>
<lb n="0422b27"/><p>此&CB00057;平旦誦七遍<note n="0422017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">夜＋（誦）【甲】</note><app n="0422017"><lem>夜</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">夜誦</rdg></app>七遍。厭魅野道<note n="0422018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蟲＝蠱【甲】</note><app n="0422018"><lem>蟲</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">蠱</rdg></app>毒
<lb n="0422b28"/>皆悉消滅。能得身心<note n="0422019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">慧＝瑟【甲】</note><app n="0422019"><lem>慧</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">瑟</rdg></app>三<note n="0422020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">解＝斛【甲】</note><app n="0422020"><lem>解</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">斛</rdg></app>脫。後生不受
<lb n="0422b29"/>生死之身。獲得法身。內外國土怨賊。一切惡
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1304.0422c" n="0422c"/>
<lb n="0422c01"/>人一切鬼神一切盜賊虎狼師子毒蟲惡獸聞
<lb n="0422c02"/>此&CB00057;聲。皆口噤閉不相惱亂。天變致厄惡夢
<lb n="0422c03"/>災殃。百鳥怪異自然消滅。此&CB00057;功能不可說
<lb n="0422c04"/>盡</p>
<lb n="0422c05"/><p>延命印　左手捻火指空指。如持蓮花。右手
<lb n="0422c06"/>直<note n="0422021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">申＝延【甲】</note><app n="0422021"><lem>申</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">延</rdg></app>如垂。真言曰</p>
<lb n="0422c07"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">引</note>摩折<anchor id="fxT21p0422c01"/>羅喻碎<note place="inline">某甲</note>娑&CB00085;<note n="0422022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">賀＝訶【甲】＊</note><app n="0422022"><lem>賀</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">訶</rdg></app></p><p type="inline">若誦此&CB00057;
<lb n="0422c08"/>延命除<note n="0422023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">災字甲本作本文</note><note n="0422023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（災）夾註＝（災）本文【甲】</note><app n="0422023"><lem><note place="inline">災</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">災</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0422c09"/><p>帝釋天印　右手作拳安腰。左<note n="0422024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">手＋（五指）【甲】</note><app n="0422024"><lem>手</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">手五指</rdg></app>直豎相著。
<lb n="0422c10"/>地水二指屈中節。以風著火背。屈空中節。真
<lb n="0422c11"/>言曰</p>
<lb n="0422c12"/><p type="dharani">唵因捺<anchor id="fxT21p0422c02"/>羅野娑&CB00085;<anchor id="fxT21p0422c03"/>賀</p><p type="inline">若誦此&CB00057;授與官位。
<lb n="0422c13"/>滿足所求</p>
<lb n="0422c14"/><p>毘沙門天印　虛心合掌。交二空並&CB00594;。二風
<lb n="0422c15"/>付二火側。如鉤端相去一寸不著。真言曰</p>
<lb n="0422c16"/><p type="dharani">唵吠室羅縛拏野娑&CB00085;<anchor id="fxT21p0422c04"/>賀</p><p type="inline">若誦此&CB00057;得大
<lb n="0422c17"/>富饒。晝夜守護</p>
<lb n="0422c18"/><p>日天真言曰</p>
<lb n="0422c19"/><p type="dharani">曩<note n="0422025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">謨＝莫【甲】</note><app n="0422025"><lem>謨</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">莫</rdg></app><anchor id="fxT21p0422c05"/>羅怛曩<note place="inline">二合</note>怛羅夜<note place="inline">引</note>野曩莫<note n="0422026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">索里＝素哩【甲】</note><app n="0422026"><lem>索里</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">素哩</rdg></app>野
<lb n="0422c20"/>薩&CB00085;曩乞灑<note place="inline">二合</note>怛<anchor id="fxT21p0422c06"/>羅<note place="inline">二合</note>羅<note n="0422027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">若＝惹【甲】</note><app n="0422027"><lem>若</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">惹</rdg></app>野唵<note place="inline">引</note>阿謨
<lb n="0422c21"/>伽<note n="0422028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">烏＝寫【甲】</note><app n="0422028"><lem>烏</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">寫</rdg></app><note place="inline">名位</note>設底娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>賀</p>
<lb n="0422c22"/><p>月天真言曰</p>
<lb n="0422c23"/><p type="dharani">唵戰<note place="inline">上</note>怛羅<note place="inline">二合</note>曩乞灑<note place="inline">二合引</note>怛羅<note place="inline">二合</note><anchor id="fxT21p0422c07"/>羅<note n="0422029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">惹＝若【甲】</note><app n="0422029"><lem>惹</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">若</rdg></app>
<lb n="0422c24"/>野<note place="inline">名位</note>設底娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>賀</p>
<lb n="0422c25"/><p>火<note n="0422030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">星＝天【甲】＊</note><app n="0422030"><lem>星</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">天</rdg></app>真言曰</p>
<lb n="0422c26"/><p type="dharani">唵阿&CB00344;<note n="0422031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">羅＋（迦）【甲】</note><app n="0422031"><lem>羅</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">羅迦</rdg></app>嚕儗野<note place="inline">名位</note><note n="0422032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">莎＝娑&CB00085;【甲】＊</note><app n="0422032"><lem>莎</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">娑&CB00085;</rdg></app>訶</p>
<lb n="0422c27"/><p>水<anchor id="fxT21p0422c08"/>星真言曰</p>
<lb n="0422c28"/><p type="dharani">唵母馱曩乞殺<note place="inline">二合</note>怛羅<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0422033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">弭＝娑&CB00085;&CB02755;【甲】</note><app n="0422033"><lem>弭</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">娑&CB00085;&CB02755;</rdg></app>曩<note place="inline">名位</note>契努摩
<lb n="0422c29"/><anchor id="fxT21p0422c09"/>莎賀</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1304.0423a" n="0423a"/>
<lb n="0423a01"/><p>木星真言曰</p>
<lb n="0423a02"/><p type="dharani">唵婆羅<note place="inline">二合</note>訶薩&CB00425;<note place="inline">二合</note>底曩摩比跢&CB00085;曩<note n="0423001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">師＝野【甲】</note><app n="0423001"><lem>師</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">野</rdg></app>
<lb n="0423a03"/><note place="inline">名位</note>摩&CB00256;&CB00085;<anchor id="fxT21p0423a01"/>羅<note place="inline">引</note>馱<note place="inline">二合</note>寧娑&CB00085;賀</p>
<lb n="0423a04"/><p>金星真言曰</p>
<lb n="0423a05"/><p type="dharani">唵<note n="0423002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">戌＋（上）夾註【甲】</note><app n="0423002"><lem>戌</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">戌<note place="inline">上</note></rdg></app>羯羅&CB00344;馱&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>羅惹野<note place="inline">名位</note>室<note n="0423003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">里＝哩【甲】＊</note><app n="0423003"><lem>里</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">哩</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0423a06"/>迦<anchor id="fxT21p0423a02"/>里娑<note n="0423004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00085;＋（二合）夾註【甲】＊</note><app n="0423004"><lem>&CB00085;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note></rdg></app>賀</p>
<lb n="0423a07"/><p>土星真言曰</p>
<lb n="0423a08"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">引</note>捨泥殺作<note place="inline">二合</note>羅曩乞殺<note place="inline">二合</note>怛<anchor id="fxT21p0423a03"/>羅<note place="inline">二合</note>跛
<lb n="0423a09"/>羅<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0423005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">訶＋（引）夾註【甲】</note><app n="0423005"><lem>訶</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">訶<note place="inline">引</note></rdg></app>摩曩嚕<note n="0423006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">波＝婆【甲】</note><app n="0423006"><lem>波</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">婆</rdg></app>野<note place="inline">名位</note>普瑟底<note place="inline">二合</note>迦<anchor id="fxT21p0423a04"/>里
<lb n="0423a10"/><anchor id="fxT21p0423a05"/>莎<note n="0423007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（二合）夾註＋訶【甲】</note><app n="0423007"><lem>訶</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho"><note place="inline">二合</note>訶</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0423a11"/><p>羅&CB00264;星真言曰</p>
<lb n="0423a12"/><p type="dharani">唵<anchor id="fxT21p0423a06"/>羅戶曩阿素<note n="0423008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">羅二合＝二合囉【甲】</note><app n="0423008"><lem>羅<note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">二合囉</rdg></app>邏惹野塞摩捨<note n="0423009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">都＝&CB00418;【甲】</note><app n="0423009"><lem>都</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB00418;</rdg></app>曩
<lb n="0423a13"/>野<note place="inline">名位</note>扇底迦<anchor id="fxT21p0423a07"/>里娑<anchor id="fxT21p0423a08"/>&CB00085;賀</p>
<lb n="0423a14"/><p>計都星真言曰</p>
<lb n="0423a15"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>計都<note n="0423010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">曩＋（曩）【甲】</note><app n="0423010"><lem>曩</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">曩曩</rdg></app>乞殺<note place="inline">二合</note>怛羅<note n="0423011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔二合〕－【甲】</note><note n="0423011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔二合〕－【甲】<corr resp="say" sic="">＊</corr></note><app n="0423011"><lem><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>邏
<lb n="0423a16"/>惹野<note place="inline">名位</note><note n="0423012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（吽）＋娑【甲】</note><note n="0423012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（吽）＋娑【甲】<corr resp="say" sic="">＊</corr></note><app n="0423012"><lem>娑</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">吽娑</rdg></app><note n="0423013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00085;＝縛【甲】＊</note><app n="0423013"><lem>&CB00085;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">縛</rdg></app>賀</p>
<lb n="0423a17"/><p>九執曜天印　堅固合掌。二空相並直&CB00594;。二
<lb n="0423a18"/>風舒。<note n="0423014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">名＝各&M062403;&M062485;【甲】</note><note n="0423014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">名＝各&M062403;【甲】，＝各&M062485;【甲】</note><app n="0423014"><lem><sic corr="各" resp="【甲】">名</sic></lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【甲】">各</rdg></app>本開立來去。真言曰</p>
<lb n="0423a19"/><p type="dharani">唵<note n="0423015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔一〕－【甲】＊</note><app n="0423015"><lem><note place="inline">一</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>&CB00617;羅<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0423016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">係＝醯二【甲】</note><app n="0423016"><lem>係</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">醯二</rdg></app>濕&CB00085;<note place="inline"><note n="0423017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔二〕－【甲】</note><app n="0423017"><lem>二</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>合二</note><anchor id="fxT21p0423a09"/>里耶<note place="inline">三</note>&CB00425;羅&CB00425;
<lb n="0423a20"/>多<note place="inline">四</note>珠<note n="0423018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">底＋（羅）&M062485;【甲】</note><sic n="0423018" corr="底羅" resp="【甲】">底</sic><note place="inline">五</note>摩野<note place="inline">六</note><anchor id="fxT21p0423a10"/>娑&CB00085;<note n="0423019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">賀＋（引）夾註【甲】</note><app n="0423019"><lem>賀</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">賀<note place="inline">引</note></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0423a21"/><p>二十八宿印　堅固合掌。並二空直立當心。
<lb n="0423a22"/>以二空召之。真言曰</p>
<lb n="0423a23"/><p type="dharani">唵諾乞灑<note place="inline">二合</note>怛羅<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0423020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB01131;＝怛【甲】</note><app n="0423020"><lem>&CB01131;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">怛</rdg></app><note place="inline">寧吉反</note>蘇那&CB00135;曳莎
<lb n="0423a24"/><note n="0423021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">訶＝賀【甲】</note><app n="0423021"><lem>訶</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">賀</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0423a25"/><p>先奉供虛空藏文殊普賢延命帝釋毘沙門等
<lb n="0423a26"/>菩薩天等。後勸請九曜二十八宿天北斗之
<lb n="0423a27"/>中本命屬星及以泰山府君司命司祿供之。
<lb n="0423a28"/>祈乞除災延命消除厄害之事。耳</p>
<lb n="0423a29"/><p>能吉祥真言曰</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1304.0423b" n="0423b"/>
<lb n="0423b01"/><p type="dharani">曩謨羅怛曩<note place="inline">二合</note>怛羅<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0423022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">夜＋（引）夾註【甲】</note><app n="0423022"><lem>夜</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">夜<note place="inline">引</note></rdg></app>野<anchor id="fxT21p0423b01"/><note place="inline">一</note>曩莫素摩
<lb n="0423b02"/>薩羅<anchor id="fxT21p0423b02"/>&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>諾訖灑<anchor id="fxT21p0423b03"/><note place="inline">二合</note>怛<note n="0423023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔羅〕－【甲】</note><app n="0423023"><lem>羅</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><anchor id="fxT21p0423b04"/><note place="inline">二合</note>邏<note place="inline">引</note>惹<note place="inline">上</note>
<lb n="0423b03"/>野者<note n="0423024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">者＝去【甲】</note><app n="0423024"><lem>者</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">去</rdg></app>都地波阿<note place="inline">去引</note>路迦羅<note n="0423025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔野〕－【甲】</note><app n="0423025"><lem>野</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>怛&CB00135;也<note place="inline"><note n="0423026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">意＝二合【甲】</note><app n="0423026"><lem>意</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">二合</rdg></app></note>
<lb n="0423b04"/>他<note n="0423027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔努〕－【甲】</note><app n="0423027"><lem>努</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0423028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">摩底跛＝麼&CB03773;底【甲】</note><app n="0423028"><lem>摩底跛</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">麼&CB03773;底</rdg></app>努摩底薩賓<note place="inline">上</note>&CB00135;佉<note place="inline">上</note>細娑&CB00085;
<lb n="0423b05"/>賀</p>
<lb n="0423b06"/><p><note n="0423029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">誦＝說【甲】</note><app n="0423029"><lem>誦</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">說</rdg></app>此九曜息災大白衣觀音陀羅尼。若日月
<lb n="0423b07"/>在人本命宮中。及五星在<note n="0423030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔本〕－【甲】</note><app n="0423030"><lem>本</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>命宮&CB00508;戰失度。
<lb n="0423b08"/>可立大<note n="0423031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">白衣＝息災&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0423031"><lem>白衣</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">息災</rdg></app>觀音或文殊八字熾盛光<note n="0423032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔佛〕－【甲】</note><app n="0423032"><lem>佛</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>頂
<lb n="0423b09"/>等道場。各依本法念誦。一切災難自然消
<lb n="0423b10"/><note n="0423033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">散＋（也）【甲】</note><app n="0423033"><lem>散</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">散也</rdg></app>。一切曜不吉祥誦此真言成能吉祥</p>
<lb n="0423b11"/><p>北斗七星真言曰</p>
<lb n="0423b12"/><p type="dharani">唵颯跢曩而<note place="inline">齒</note>曩野伴惹<note n="0423034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">密＋（惹）【甲】</note><app n="0423034"><lem>密</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">密惹</rdg></app>野<note place="inline">二合</note>染普他摩
<lb n="0423b13"/>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>弭曩<note place="inline">名位</note><anchor id="fxT21p0423b05"/>羅訖山婆&CB00085;都<anchor id="fxT21p0423b06"/>莎<note n="0423035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">訶＝賀引【甲】</note><app n="0423035"><lem>訶</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">賀引</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0423b14"/><p>若羅<note n="0423036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00264;＝曜【甲】</note><app n="0423036"><lem>&CB00264;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">曜</rdg></app>計都暗行人本命星宮。須誦此北斗
<lb n="0423b15"/>真言。一切如來說。破一切宿曜<note n="0423037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔障〕－【甲】</note><app n="0423037"><lem>障</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>吉祥。真
<lb n="0423b16"/>言曰</p>
<lb n="0423b17"/><p type="dharani">唵薩羅&CB00085;諾剎怛<anchor id="fxT21p0423b07"/>羅<note place="inline">二合</note>三<note n="0423038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">摩＝麼【甲】</note><app n="0423038"><lem>摩</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">麼</rdg></app>曳室<anchor id="fxT21p0423b08"/>里曳扇
<lb n="0423b18"/>底迦<note n="0423039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔俱〕－【甲】</note><app n="0423039"><lem>俱</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>嚕娑&CB00085;<note n="0423040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">賀＝二合賀引【甲】</note><app n="0423040"><lem>賀</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">二合賀引</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0423b19"/><p>金剛<note n="0423041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">宿＝大【甲】</note><app n="0423041"><lem>宿</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">大</rdg></app>成就經。吉祥成就品<note n="0423042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">曰＝云【甲】</note><app n="0423042"><lem>曰</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">云</rdg></app>。我今宣說
<lb n="0423b20"/>世間成就<note n="0423043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（最）＋妙【甲】</note><app n="0423043"><lem>妙</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">最妙</rdg></app>祕法。如是諸曜運行虛空。若一
<lb n="0423b21"/>若二三四五等。臨入眾生命宿對衝宿遷移
<lb n="0423b22"/>宿大殺<note n="0423044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（宿）＋業【甲】</note><app n="0423044"><lem>業</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">宿業</rdg></app>宿安宿薄相宿奴婢宿。作諸厄害。
<lb n="0423b23"/>四大惡曜。所謂火曜土曜羅&CB00264;計都最重眾
<lb n="0423b24"/>生。是時修諸福業廣施<note n="0423045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">仁慈＝慈仁【甲】</note><app n="0423045"><lem>仁慈</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">慈仁</rdg></app>。或依文殊八字
<lb n="0423b25"/>真言。<note n="0423046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">或＋（又）【甲】</note><app n="0423046"><lem>或</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">或又</rdg></app>依熾盛光佛頂。或依被葉衣觀音。
<lb n="0423b26"/>或依一字王佛頂。立<note n="0423047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">大＝火【甲】</note><app n="0423047"><lem>大</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">火</rdg></app>息災護摩壇場。各
<lb n="0423b27"/>依本法念誦供養。一切災難自然消滅。作成
<lb n="0423b28"/>就法於心宿直日柳宿直日昴宿直日牛宿直
<lb n="0423b29"/>日。不簡日月吉凶。但於此宿直日於一日之
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1304.0423c" n="0423c"/>
<lb n="0423c01"/>中。不食念誦滿一千八<note n="0423048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔十〕－【甲】</note><app n="0423048"><lem>十</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>遍。所有心願應時
<lb n="0423c02"/>便<note n="0423049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">渴＝得【甲】</note><app n="0423049"><lem>渴</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">得</rdg></app>大悉地。若厄難時。於本生日最<note n="0423050" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（為）＋相【甲】</note><app n="0423050"><lem>相</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">為相</rdg></app>應。
<lb n="0423c03"/>若作木曜成就法者。月十六日最為相應。若
<lb n="0423c04"/>作火曜成<note n="0423051" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">就＝熟【甲】＊</note><app n="0423051"><lem>就</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">熟</rdg></app>法者。即彼直日最為相應。若作
<lb n="0423c05"/>土曜成<anchor id="fxT21p0423c01"/>就法者。每月七日最為相應。若作金
<lb n="0423c06"/>曜成就法者。隨所見方平<note n="0423052" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">旦＋（最為相應若作金曜成就法者隨所見方平旦）【甲】</note><app n="0423052"><lem>旦</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">旦最為相應若作金曜成就法者隨所見方平旦</rdg></app><note n="0423053" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">最為相應＝為勝【甲】</note><app n="0423053"><lem>最為相應</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">為勝</rdg></app>。若
<lb n="0423c07"/>作水曜成就法者依水曜直日而作成就。若
<lb n="0423c08"/>作羅&CB00264;計都法者。依本生<note n="0423054" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（星）＋日【甲】</note><app n="0423054"><lem>日</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">星日</rdg></app>以為相應。若復
<lb n="0423c09"/>供養本<note n="0423055" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">生＝星【甲】</note><app n="0423055"><lem>生</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">星</rdg></app>宿者。於本生年<note n="0423056" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">月＝日【甲】</note><app n="0423056"><lem>月</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">日</rdg></app>。若本生日而
<lb n="0423c10"/>可取成就。若惡宿生每月供養。若三<note n="0423057" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">日＋（五日）【甲】</note><app n="0423057"><lem>日</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">日五日</rdg></app>七日
<lb n="0423c11"/>供<note n="0423058" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">養＋（惡曜）【甲】</note><app n="0423058"><lem>養</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">養惡曜</rdg></app>直轉成吉祥直。祕勿令知<note n="0423059" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">俗＋（人）【甲】</note><app n="0423059"><lem>俗</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">俗人</rdg></app>也<note n="0423060" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此下甲本奧書云康元二年二月晦日於覺洞院中寫之了觀尊二十二</note></p>
